Zone Labs is aware of a recent report of an issue with the 
ZoneAlarm Pro inbound mail protection feature.

This report is currently being investigated.  Zone Labs 
will issue a formal response at the earliest opportunity.

Zone Labs takes the security of our products very 
seriously and examines any security report thoroughly.

Questions or comments about this issue, or to report any 
other issue in Zone Labs products or services, should be 
directed to security@...elabs.com.

John LaCour
Zone Labs Product Security Team

